## Screenshot Tips

- Use a real device or a simulator at exact resolution — don't upscale.
- Populate the app with realistic (but anonymised) data before taking screenshots.
- Show the app in light mode (dark mode screenshots are optional extras).
- Remove personal data — use names like "Acme Corp", "Jane S.", "Project Alpha".
- On iOS: use `xcrun simctl io booted screenshot screenshot.png` to capture at exact resolution.
- On Android: use `adb shell screencap -p /sdcard/shot.png && adb pull /sdcard/shot.png`.
